OL,3,CThe Voice of Hind Rajab: A film about
OL,4,Ca child the world heard too late
OL,6,FThe Tunisian filmmaker has faced
OL,7,Fcriticisms of exploitation, but says
OL,8,Fhiring a child to mimic Hind's voice
OL,9,Fwas unthinkable, as the aim was to
OL,10,Fhonour Hind's voice, ITV News Arts
OL,11,FEditor Nina Nannar reports
OL,13,FWhen I saw The Voice of Hind Rajab at
OL,14,Fa screening, the closing credits went
OL,15,Fup, and the cinema was in total
OL,16,Fsilence. Save for the sound of sobs.
OL,18,FWe stayed silent for minutes; there
OL,19,Fwas no applause or standing ovation
OL,20,Fthat you can sometimes get at special
OL,21,Fscreenings, which precede a Q&A.
