OL,3,CThe Voice of Hind Rajab: A film about
OL,4,Ca child the world heard too late
OL,6,FThere was just stunned silence. It's
OL,7,Fthat kind of film.
OL,9,FThe subject matter is harrowing. A
OL,10,Ffive-year-old Palestinian girl is
OL,11,Ftrapped in a car in Northern Gaza with
OL,12,Fthe bodies of six of her family, all
OL,13,Fkilled in an Israeli attack.
OL,15,FHind Rajab somehow manages to speak to
OL,16,FRed Crescent workers in their office
OL,17,Fin Ramallah, who then spend the next
OL,18,Ffew hours trying to rescue her.
