OL,3,CThe Voice of Hind Rajab: A film about
OL,4,Ca child the world heard too late
OL,6,FThe story made worldwide headlines in
OL,7,FJanuary 2024, when the recording of
OL,8,Fthe voice of the little girl was
OL,9,Freleased by the Red Crescent, an
OL,10,Forganisation affiliated with the Red
OL,11,FCross.
OL,13,FIn it, Hind asks time and again for
OL,14,Fsomeone to come and get her. She is a
OL,15,Fchild and cannot understand, of
OL,16,Fcourse, the web of bureaucracy
OL,17,Finvolved in getting permission for an
OL,18,Fambulance to drive to where she is.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
