OL,3,CThe Voice of Hind Rajab: A film about
OL,4,Ca child the world heard too late
OL,6,FThe humanitarian organisation cannot
OL,7,Fdeal with the Israel Defence Force
OL,8,Fdirectly but must go through
OL,9,Fintermediaries.
OL,11,FIt takes more than three hours, during
OL,12,Fwhich time you listen as the terrified
OL,13,Flittle girl begs for someone to save
OL,14,Fher life.
OL,16,FHind was killed, and the two ambulance
OL,17,Fworkers sent to rescue her also died
OL,18,Fwhen their vehicle was bombed, just
OL,19,Fbefore they reached her.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
