OL,3,CThe Voice of Hind Rajab: A film about
OL,4,Ca child the world heard too late
OL,6,FThe IDF, which initially said it
OL,7,Fhadn't been in the area at the time,
OL,8,Ftold us they are still investigating
OL,9,Fthe incident.
OL,11,FWhat film director Kaouther Ben Hania
OL,12,Fwants is accountability.
OL,14,FAnd so she decided to make her
OL,15,Fdocudrama of the event. And in a
OL,16,Fcontroversial decision, decided that
OL,17,Fher actors would be performing
OL,18,Falongside the real voice of Hind.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
