OL,3,CThe Voice of Hind Rajab: A film about
OL,4,Ca child the world heard too late
OL,6,FIn the scenes in which you see them
OL,7,Fspeaking on the phone, the voice you
OL,8,Fhear coming back is the real one,
OL,9,Fwhich makes the viewing of this film
OL,10,Fincredibly powerful. And heartbreaking.
OL,12,FThe Tunisian filmmaker has faced
OL,13,Fcriticisms of exploitation, but says
OL,14,Fhiring a child to mimic Hind's voice
OL,15,Fwas unthinkable, as the aim was to
OL,16,Fhonour Hind's voice.
