OL,3,CThe Voice of Hind Rajab: A film about
OL,4,Ca child the world heard too late
OL,6,FShe says Hind's mother supported the
OL,7,Fdecision to use the real recordings.
OL,8,FNow evacuated from Gaza, she is
OL,9,Fdetermined that her daughter's death
OL,10,Fcannot be forgotten, one of the
OL,11,Festimated 20,000 children who have
OL,12,Fbeen killed in the war there.
OL,14,FIndeed, Wesam Hamada introduced The
OL,15,FVoice of Hind Rajab when it was
OL,16,Fscreened recently at the Doha Film
OL,17,FFestival.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
