OL,3,CThe Voice of Hind Rajab: A film about
OL,4,Ca child the world heard too late
OL,6,FThere are many children like Hind,
OL,7,Fsays Ben Hania, but she saw an
OL,8,Fopportunity to shout about the
OL,9,Fkilling, using her power as a
OL,10,Ffilmmaker, and in a way, highlighting
OL,11,Fthe larger death toll.
OL,13,FIt is a bold move, film has had
OL,14,Fextraordinary reviews.
OL,16,FIt is a tough watch, as you know where
OL,17,Fit's going. And you'll never forget
OL,18,Fthe experience.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/8
